                "text": "A hazard response crew can spend 1 Resolve Point as a swift action to change either one type of energy damage dealt by one of their weapons into another energy type, or change their energy resistance to resist a different type of energy. This ability can affect and apply to only the following energy types: acid, cold, electricity, fire, and sonic. Either effect lasts for 1d4+1 rounds.",
